# Mersenne-prime

Generate Mersenne prime numbers into files (C++)

# Prerequisites

FLINT: https://flintlib.org/downloads.html
(Files generated with FLINT 3.1.0)

# Compile

g++ -o mersenne-prime mersenne-prime.cpp -L/usr/local/lib -lflint

# Execute

./mersenne-prime
